== Introduction ==
Opendaylight dlux is a new UI for controller using AngularJS as base front end technology. It will be a more interactive UI, mostly based on the client side technologies, provide a replacement of existing UI of the controller.
Existing controller UI might be deprecated. Controller will only expose APIs to be consumed by UI or other applications. It will help controller to be become leaner and concise.
New UI will mostly consume MD-SAL based RESTConf APIs. 
